## what is the [hacker](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is) [[hive|hive0]]?

the [hacker](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is) [[hive|hive0]] is an invitation to all [hackers](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is) at [UC Berkeley](http://berkeley.edu) to influence the [Berkeley Student Cooperative](http://bsc.coop) through [hacking](http://www.catb.org/esr/faqs/hacker-howto.html#what_is), in the spirit of the international communities known as [hackerspaces](http://hackerspaces.org/wiki/List_of_Hacker_Spaces).

